headline: Stocks to Watch Tuesday: Applied Digital, Meta, Newmont, Pop Mart
summary: ↗️ Applied Digital (APLD): The artificial-intelligence infrastructure provider plans to spin out its cloud business and combine it with EKSO Bionics (EKSO). Shares in Applied Digital rose 2% in premarket trading, while EKSO shares surged around 40%.
